                     <title type="supplied" xml:lang="da">Skånske lov</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="da">Old Danish</textLang>
                     <incipit>For ma<ex>n</ex> kone oc dør ha<ex>n</ex>
                        <lb/> før en hun for barn / oc <lb/> sigh<ex>e</ex>r hun oc he<ex>n</ex>nes
                           fre<ex>n</ex>
                        <lb rend="hyphenated"/>dher ath hun ær m<ex>eth</ex> barn <lb/> tha skal hun
